metadata.description:
Relaxed from the world.
Half submerged, she stays slightly above the surface.
The model's unique position reinforces the impression of lifelong relaxation.
I'm resting, I'm safe. You can join me.

IMAGE | Squint your eyes to see the spatial value of this work.
Oil on canvas, technique of intense, strong brushstrokes.

ONE ORIGINAL | Image signed on front and back by EK.
Author's Certificate of Authenticity will be included.

Technical Notes: 
- Top quality branded oil paints used. Canvas stretched on a wooden frame. Protection with a coating of satin varnish.
- The painting is ready to hang on the wall without a frame (the sides are painted) or in a frame of your choice. It will always look great.
- The colors of the artwork may look different due to the screen settings.
